platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: ジュラシック・パークをレゴで再現

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When dinosaurs collide with LEGO bricks, you don’t have to be Mr. DNA to know the result is pure fun. Starring characters and creatures from all four Jurassic Park movies, this fantastic adventure lets you relive your favorite moments from the series and even create new ones with your own custom dinos. Full of all the humor, action, and surprises you expect, it’s a wacky team-up of T-Rex proportions.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 「ジュラシック・パーク」シリーズ全4作をレゴで再現したアクションゲーム。
